&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Go global with Ogilvy:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt; As part of a leading global network, you&#39;ll have access to exciting career pathways and opportunities around the world. Expand your horizons and connect with colleagues across the globe.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233279&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Family &amp;amp; caregiver support: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We offer a gender-neutral parental leave policy, providing 16 weeks of p

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We are a team. We are accountable. We partner with our clients to deliver strategic creative we are proud of.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We learn together, we create together, we win together.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;And most importantly, we have fun together.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Strong&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Strong&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Ogilvy Sydney is looking for Creative Teams with a passion for bold ideas and a drive to create work that earns attention, shapes culture and solves real business problems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;We’re looking for Art Directors and Copywriters who are curious, ambitious and excited to push their craft further. Whether you’re at the start of your career or have a few years of experience,&amp;nbsp; this is a role for people who want to make work that matters. You’ll be encouraged to challenge briefs, think beyond the obvious and bring fresh energy to every stage of the creative process — from first idea through to final execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Strong&quot;&gt;What &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Strong&quot;&gt;you’ll&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Strong&quot;&gt; do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Strong&quot;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the development of creative ideas and campaigns across multiple channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Think conceptually and help solve client business challenges through creativity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Creative Directors, strategists, designers and client teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present and communicate ideas clearly and confidently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring a strong attention to detail across design, copy and presentation materials&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay curious about culture, technology, social platforms and emerging trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously develop your creative craft and push your thinking further&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll bring:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-spread=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A portfolio that demonstrates strong thinking, craft and creative potential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in an agency or similar creative environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to develop ideas that work across 360 campaigns and platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication, collaboration and storytelling skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proactive attitude and willingness to get stuck in&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A sense of humour, resilience and genuine passion for creativity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whether you’re early in your career or already operating at mid-weight level, we’re looking for creatives who want to grow, contribute meaningfully to great work and be part of a team that’s shaping what’s next.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Why Ogilvy?  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We have an opportunity for a Digital Producer to join our national team to lead the end-to-end delivery of email marketing campaigns across several top-tier retail clients.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:2}&quot;&gt;About Ogilvy One&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ogilvy One is the customer experience and engagement arm of Ogilvy, specialising in building valuable relationships by design.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For 25 years, we&#39;ve transformed business challenges into human-centric solutions that drive long-term customer value, always putting creativity at the heart of our approach. Across Ogilvy&#39;s global network of 120+ offices, we combine creativity, data, and AI to craft personalized brand experiences that connect with customers on a deeper level.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With over 4,000 specialists bringing expertise in creative, strategy, data, media, and technology, supported by a network of technology hubs powered by Verticurl, we deliver integrated solutions that help brands thrive in the age of personalization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-charstyle=&quot;Strong&quot;&gt;About the role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a&amp;nbsp;Digital Producer to lead the end-to-end delivery of data-driven email marketing campaigns across several top-tier retail clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working within one of Australia’s leading MarTech and Digital Experience teams, you will own the planning, production and execution of multi-channel campaign&lt;strong&gt;s&lt;/strong&gt; across marketing automation platforms such as Salesforce Marketing Cloud and Braze.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role sits at the centre of delivery – translating strategy into executable plans, coordinating designers and developers, managing campaign production and ensuring all outputs meet quality, timeline and performance expectations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with clients, strategists and technical specialists to deliver high-quality digital campaigns that drive measurable results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role could be based in Melbourne or Sydney, but Melbourne is preferred.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
