&lt;li&gt;Coordinate cross-functional teams to ensure campaigns are&amp;nbsp;delivered on time, within scope and to the required quality standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage campaign production workflows using tools such as&amp;nbsp;Jira, Wrike, Monday.com or similar platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Client &amp;amp; Stakeholder Management&lt;/p&gt;
