&lt;li&gt;Act as the day-to-day delivery lead for clients, ensuring campaign requirements, timelines and expectations are clearly understood.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run campaign briefings and align stakeholders across strategy, creative and technology teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage campaign scope and timelines while proactively addressing risks and delivery challenges.&lt;/li&gt;
